From 0e18de91713ce10a2db60b198b720e40d7d500c0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ray <hello@ramonclaudio.com>
Date: Sat, 2 May 2026 14:46:31 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] [iOS][ui] Add SwiftUI Alert component

Wraps SwiftUI's .alert(_:isPresented:actions:message:) modifier with the same Trigger / Actions / Message slot model used by ConfirmationDialog. Replaces the existing AlertDialogScreen.ios.tsx 'Not implemented yet' placeholder with a working demo and registers it in UIScreen.ios.tsx.
